data.title: 1958) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Yoncalla Woman Dies In Hospital Tuesday Cecile Fay Marston, 70, of Yoncalla, died at Cottage Grove Hospital Tuesday night. She was born Feb. 13, 1888 at Alba, Neb., and came to Oregon when a small child with her parents. During her life she lived at Ashland, Medford and Eugene and moved to Douglas County 12 years ago....
